{"tid":2103138,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"人血饅頭 | 潮語字典","createTime":"2020-07-11T04:01:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T04:01:51.000Z","uid":72980,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"13608898e3f6725ddfa5df3dafe9da9e2d44d727","tid":2103138,"uid":72980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:01:51.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭<br />\n<br />\n更新日期: 2019-12-14<br />\n<br />\n意思<br />\n<br />\n「人血饅頭」指抗爭者的鮮血。<br />\n「吃人血饅頭」是指以抗爭者的鮮血來達至某些目的。<br />\n<br />\n起源<br />\n<br />\n出自魯迅的短篇小說《藥》。小說中革命者被處決後，鮮血被用來製成人血饅頭，傳聞指人血饅頭能醫百病。<br />\n<br />\n例句<br />\n<br />\n不少政客在吃著抗爭者的人血饅頭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkdic.my-helper.com/%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%80%E9%A5%85%E9%A0%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkdic.my-helper.com%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A1%2580%25E9%25A5%2585%25E9%25A0%25AD%2F&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyBdyOQTk4RMct2Rsqyof94c%3D&h=607dacfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkdic.my-helper.com/%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%80%E9%A5%85%E9%A0%AD/</a>"}]}